OL,3,CCrochet expert's giant doily helps win
OL,4,CTurner Prize
OL,6,FITV News' Anna Youssef spoke to
OL,7,FRachael about how it feels to see her
OL,8,Fwork in a Turner Prize-winning
OL,9,Finstallation.
OL,11,FA crochet expert hopes the five metre
OL,12,Fwide doily she was commissioned to
OL,13,Fcreate will make people "recognise
OL,14,Fcrochet as an art", after it made up
OL,15,Fpart of a Turner Prize winning art
OL,16,Finstallation.
