OL,3,CCrochet expert's giant doily helps win
OL,4,CTurner Prize
OL,6,FRachael Mills, who leads crochet
OL,7,Fclasses in Blackburn and owns her own
OL,8,Fbusiness, was contacted by artist
OL,9,FJasleen Kaur in 2022 to create an
OL,10,Fornamental doily mat as part of her
OL,11,Fexhibition in Glasgow; Alter Altar.
OL,13,FRachael said: "She phoned me to make
OL,14,Fthe doily and gave me just a
OL,15,Fphotograph of a six inch doily."
OL,17,FThe installation, which focused on
OL,18,FKaur's experience growing up in
OL,19,FGlasgow's Sikh community, featured the
OL,20,Fdoily thrown over her father's first
OL,21,Fcar: a red vintage Ford Escort.
