OL,3,CCrochet expert's giant doily helps win
OL,4,CTurner Prize
OL,6,FRachael, 56, said the doily required
OL,7,F67 balls of cotton yarn took around
OL,8,Fthree months to complete.
OL,10,FShe said: "It had to cover the car so
OL,11,Fit had to be quite huge. I used to
OL,12,Ftake it in the pub down the road and
OL,13,Flay it on the dance floor just to take
OL,14,Fa photo and make sure the pattern was
OL,15,Fworking."
