OL,3,CCrochet expert's giant doily helps win
OL,4,CTurner Prize
OL,6,FA doily is a small, decorative mat
OL,7,Ftypically made of fabric or paper.
OL,8,FAccording to Kaur, the doily
OL,9,Frepresents "the legacies of Empire,
OL,10,Fcotton and migration from ex-colonies
OL,11,Fto British mills after the second
OL,12,Fworld war."
OL,14,FThe red Ford Escort represents the
OL,15,Fpoverty in which Kaur grew up, in
OL,16,Fwhich just owning a car was seen as a
OL,17,Fstatus symbol.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
