OL,3,CCrochet expert's giant doily helps win
OL,4,CTurner Prize
OL,6,FAt a ceremony on Tuesday 3 December
OL,7,Fthe installation won the Turner Prize,
OL,8,Fwhich celebrates a British visual
OL,9,Fartist under the age of 50.
OL,11,FRosie Cooper, director of Wysing Arts
OL,12,FCentre, who sits on the judging panel
OL,13,Fsaid Jasleen sees the vehicle as a
OL,14,F"representation of her dad's first car
OL,15,Fand his migrant desires" and it
OL,16,F"blasted snippets of uplifting pop
OL,17,Fsongs referencing freedom and
OL,18,Fliberation throughout the space".
