OL,3,CCrochet expert's giant doily helps win
OL,4,CTurner Prize
OL,6,FAt the age of 38, Jasleen Kaur is the
OL,7,Fyoungest ever artist to win the prize
OL,8,Fand will take home #40,000 along with
OL,9,Fthe accolade.
OL,11,FFor Rachael, it is enough to know the
OL,12,Fart of crocheting is being recognised
OL,13,Fby the art world.
OL,15,FShe said: "Most people don't put art
OL,16,Fand crochet together but it is an art
OL,17,Fform."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
