OL,3,CCrochet expert's giant doily helps win
OL,4,CTurner Prize
OL,6,FThe Turner Prize, named after the
OL,7,FBritish painter JMW Turner, is the
OL,8,Fmost high-profile award in British art
OL,9,Fand this year it celebrates its 40th
OL,10,Fanniversary.
OL,12,FPrevious winners include Anish Kapoor,
OL,13,FSteve McQueen, Gillian Wearing, Antony
OL,14,FGormley, Grayson Perry, Jeremy Deller,
OL,15,FHelen Marten and Veronica Ryan.
OL,17,FAlter Altar is currently on display at
OL,18,Fthe Tate Britain in London until 16
OL,19,FFebruary 2025.
